main event: A UFO report was filed in July 1959 regarding an image of a landscape depicting a body of water surrounded by mountains and clouds.
interesting points: The report includes a description of a black and white photograph,The image does not show any human figure,The photograph depicts a natural landscape rather than a UFO sighting,The report is classified as unclassified by the FOREIGN TECHNOLOGY DIVISION.AFSC, The reporting location is in Switzerland.
sighted object: black and white photograph of a landscape
